Third Department,

August, 1971

(August 10, 1971) The People of the State of New York ex rel. George Ludwig, Petitioner, v. Joseph P. Conboy, as Superintendent of Great Meadow Correctional Facility, Respondent.

Application, pursuant to CPLR 7002 (subd. [b], par. 2), for a writ of habeas corpus denied as insufficient on its face. Herlihy, P. J., Reynolds, Staley, Jr., Greenblott and Sweeney, JJ., concur.
